    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hi! These Are Your Eyeballs is a monotonous game in which you have to work as a courier delivering eyeballs for 9 days. The biggest challenge this game has to offer is time management. Average playthrough time is ~2 hours.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/9114125c7eef5500cfa99d70a35b627f.poster.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/9114125c7eef5500cfa99d70a35b627f.webm?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/9114125c7eef5500cfa99d70a35b627f.mp4?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/e16f53f9cf7280c217797431fd802515.webp?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the gloomy and oppressive panel houses of the post-Soviet landscape, residents <strong>have lost the light</strong> of their lives and are doomed to exist in darkness. You are the courier for EyeBallStore, and only you can deliver new eyeballs to the inhabitants of Limbo Alley, giving them a chance to see the world anew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is straightforward — deliver orders <strong>on time</strong>. But it's not that simple: delays are almost  unacceptable, and each time you fail to meet the deadline, your clients' <strong>hope</strong> for a better life fades even more. You have <strong>nine</strong> shifts to help the residents of Limbo Alley. Each new day is tougher than the last, but it all depends on how you approach your mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to shoulder this burden and face what's waiting for you?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/95b1fd58333942203591104a138d23d3.webp?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/b374e55b0f1ad38cac449a05b0b5c025.poster.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/b374e55b0f1ad38cac449a05b0b5c025.webm?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/b374e55b0f1ad38cac449a05b0b5c025.mp4?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every resident of Limbo Alley has their own story and reasons for <strong>losing the light in their eyes</strong>, but not everyone is willing to share it openly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/e4d96785f3010c32bfb4093ec055fa8b.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/296639d275abed3b43cd6138e697c8f8.poster.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/296639d275abed3b43cd6138e697c8f8.webm?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/296639d275abed3b43cd6138e697c8f8.mp4?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore gray panel buildings where every corridor is steeped in <strong>despair</strong>. Along the way, you may experience a <strong>warm</strong> yet inexplicable nostalgia from the atmosphere of Limbo Alley.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/72443b94fff02ed58f817c094469276a.webp?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/07de13860fb1837735f3a1adf17f4c8f.poster.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/07de13860fb1837735f3a1adf17f4c8f.webm?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/07de13860fb1837735f3a1adf17f4c8f.mp4?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For completed deliveries, you'll receive a literally <strong>meager</strong> reward, which can be spent at the EyeBallStore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/cd86dfb2324f130b765a0796e29cfb90.poster.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/cd86dfb2324f130b765a0796e29cfb90.webm?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/cd86dfb2324f130b765a0796e29cfb90.mp4?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whenever possible, acquire new items and upgrades — they'll help you fulfill orders faster and more efficiently!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/30a9bac5d4b3c07a28cf80b535163ccc.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/c4cfcbcc9342caa9763b5be99f331cae.poster.avif?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/c4cfcbcc9342caa9763b5be99f331cae.webm?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/c4cfcbcc9342caa9763b5be99f331cae.mp4?t=1732015232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delays over time can lead to negative consequences for the residents and, consequently, for your final shift. <strong>Everything is in your hands — including the orders.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121800/extras/578271393e2d0b85c65ad8683e0217be.webp?t=1732015232\" width=600 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The creation of this game was inspired by a theme that has been simmering in my friend's and my minds for years — the fading of the human spirit. We observed this even as children when we looked at adults, and we see it two decades later when we look at ourselves. Things in the world and society change; new circumstances and details emerge; some things get better, others worse, but internal human struggles retain their essence across generations.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is, in many ways, a reflection on how, through simple yet abstract means, one might help a fading person see the world anew, soothe traumas accumulated over the years, and try to love life once again.</i></p>",
